<HEADLINE> Tanzania Alert on Tax Evasion </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DAR ES SALAAM, August 20 (Xinhua) -- Tanzania's Minister of
Finance Daniel Yona has directed the Tanzania Revenue Authority
(TRA) to become vigilant against massive tax evasion.
</P>
