<TEXT>
<P>
HARARE, August 21 (Xinhua) -- Brazil's Oswald Cruz foundation
is to collaborate with the World Health Organization (WHO) in
strengthening the human resource base and institutional capacity
in the health sector of Africa's five Portuguese countries.
</P>
<P>
