support to WHO's comprehensive 20-year plan for human resources
development and institutional capacity-building in the health
sector of the five African countries," he said.
</P>
<P>
The plan, which comes into effect next July, also envisages the
 introduction of measures that will respond to future needs of
national health services in the respective countries. 
