<HEADLINE> Macao Holds International Beer Carnival </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MACAO, August 21 (Xinhua) -- A two-day international beer
carnival, the second of its kind held in Macao, was launched here
Saturday afternoon.
</P>
<P>
Colorful stands were set up in a downtown square to exhibit 12
kinds of beer made in the inland areas of China, Hong Kong and
Taiwan regions, the Untied States, Mexico, Germany, the
Netherlands, Britain, Singapore and Thailand.
</P>
