<HEADLINE> Local Driver Takes Lead in Finland Rally </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HELSINKI, August 20 (Xinhua) -- Local driver Marcus Gronholm
took the lead Friday in the Neste Rally Finland at Jyvaskyla.
