cooperation documents in Beijing on Wednesday during Malaysian
Prime Minister Datuk Seri Mahathir bin Mohamad's China visit.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese Academy of Sciences and the Chinese Academy of
Engineering Sciences respectively signed a memorandum with
Malaysia's Academy of Sciences on cooperation in science,
engineering and technology.
</P>
<P>
